General.Name: Avation PLC
General.Description: Avation PLC, together with its subsidiaries, leases commercial passenger aircraft to airlines worldwide. The company's fleet includes 14 narrow-body jets, two twin-aisle jets, and 23 ATR 72 twin-engine turboprop aircraft. As of June 30, 2022, the company owned and managed a fleet of 39 aircraft. It is also involved in the financing business. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Singapore.
